{
  "stem": "1216.2",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "That I really-- the recall doesn't go that far, partly because as we went very slowly into this registration building-- it was just a wooden barracks, as they all were, most of them were in Westerbork-- my mother made me sit down on a chair a little off to the side and said, now you stay there, and we'll come back for you.",
      "word_count": 63
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "The only problem was that everybody went into this big barracks, and I didn't see anybody come out.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I got scared, and, of course, I started crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I was age 10 by then.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they had disappeared in this barracks.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I heard noises in there.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I heard voices, but nobody was coming out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What I didn't know, of course, was that they came out on the other end.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So some adult-- some man whom I didn't know and who didn't know me-- finally saw me, wanted to know what was happening, which I told him.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he then took me in and found my mother for me.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I do not know how.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And my mother was most upset.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Why are you crying?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "We told you we would come back for you.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And all I could say was well, I didn't know whether you were ever coming back.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So that was the beginning of Westerbork.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And during that registration, we were assigned to a barracks.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were all very long.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They looked like, oh, temporary buildings do here.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Made of wood, very long, and very low, with really one great big room on either side of the entrance which was in the middle, with-- together with a little hallway.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And the men slept on the one side.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "The women slept on the other side.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
